{"type":"message","id":"abbc1e8d","parentId":"281879e4","timestamp":"2026-03-15T00:36:50.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've done extensive manual exploration and haven't found any JSON files containing the specified patterns. Given the limitations of the tools available (can't create exec sessions to run search commands), I should provide my findings to the main agent.\n\nLet me compile my final report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 任务完成报告\n\n### 搜索范围\n在 `C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw` 目录下递归查找所有 .json 文件，并搜索包含以下内容的文件：\n- \"apply_patch\"\n- \"tools.profile\"\n- \"coding\" 和 \"allowlist\"（同时包含）\n\n### 找到的 JSON 文件\n在 `C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw` 目录下仅找到 **2 个 JSON 文件**：\n\n1. **`C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\extensions\\openclaw-tavily\\package.json`**\n   - 内容：标准的 npm 包配置文件\n   - 包含：包名、版本、依赖、脚本等\n   - **不包含**目标搜索模式\n\n2. **`C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\extensions\\openclaw-tavily\\openclaw.plugin.json`**\n   - 内容：Tavily Search 插件配置\n   - 包含：插件 ID、配置 schema、UI 提示等\n   - **不包含**目标搜索模式\n\n### 搜索结果\n**未找到**任何包含以下模式的 JSON 文件：\n- ❌ \"apply_patch\"\n- ❌ \"tools.profile\"\n- ❌ \"coding\" + \"allowlist\"（同时出现）\n\n### 说明\n由于 `process` 工具无法创建新的 exec 会话（系统显示 \"No running or recent sessions\" 且所有会话操作均返回 \"No active session found\"），无法使用 PowerShell 命令进行自动化递归搜索。以上结果基于手动探索常见配置目录得出。\n\n### 建议\n如需更彻底的搜索，建议：\n1. 检查 exec 会话创建机制是否正常\n2. 或手动运行以下 PowerShell 命令：\n   ```powershell\n   Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\" -Recurse -Filter \"*.json\" -File | \n   ForEach-Object { \n       $content = Get-Content $_.FullName -Raw\n       if ($content -match \"apply_patch\" -or $content -match \"tools\\.profile\" -or ($content -match \"coding\" -and $content -match \"allowlist\")) {\n           $_.FullName\n       }\n   }\n   ```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773535004316}}
